    "body": "This PR adds support for PLaMo2, specifically [PLaMo2 1B](https://huggingface.co/pfnet/plamo-2-1b) and [PLaMo2 8B](https://huggingface.co/pfnet/plamo-2-8b). PLaMo2 is a hybrid [mamba2](https://github.com/state-spaces/mamba) architecture featuring sliding window attention.\n\nIn this PR, we have created the inference architecture for the PLaMo2 model.\n\nPlease note that some functionalities such as PP/TP, quantization, and LoRA are not yet supported in this PR. We plan to address these features in subsequent follow-up PRs. ",
